		   <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform2><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=139422"><span id=Scholar>Mxyzptlk</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br>23 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>As BrooksaMillion mentioned, there is a large selection of weapons to choose from that will &quot;beat out&quot; your fists. However, even if you can not find a weapon that you can afford that will &quot;beat out&quot; your fists, it is always a good idea to grin and bear the fact that you are not doing the maximum damage you are capable of and use an inferior 1hb or 2hb weapon to keep your skills up to par with your level. You never know when you will come across that really nice 1hb or 2hb weapon for cheap or for free. If you do happen to come across that Cane of Tranquil for free one day and you have almost no skill in 1hb, believe me, you <b>WILL</b> be kicking yourself in the backside.&nbsp;&nbsp;I will list a few weapons below and their approximate prices on my server (Vazaelle). These may not all &quot;beat out&quot; your fists, but they are good weapons to acquire either because they are common or inexpensive.<br>               <br>               <u><b>One-Hand Bash:</b></u> <br><b>Fighting Baton:</b>  Dmg 8, Dly 20. +2.00 Wt   <br>This weapon is found in the Crypt of Dalnir off of a mob called Lumpy Goo. This weapon costs 250-400pp.<br><br><b>Sarnak Enforcer:</b> Dmg 7, Dly 28. +1.50 Wt<br>This weapon is also found in the Crypt of Dalnir off of either An Undead Smith, or A Coerced PenKeeper. This weapon costs 20-50pp.<br><br><b>Cane of the Tranquil:</b> Dmg 11, Dly 25. +2.50 Wt<br>This weapon is found in Old Sebilis off of Necrosis Scarab. This weapon costs 400-600pp.<br><br><b>Blackjack:</b> Dmg 7, Dly 21. +1.90 Wt <br>This weapon is found in Karnor's Castle off of either Spectral Protector or Spectral Knight. This weapon costs 100-200pp.<br><br><br>               <u><b>Two-hand Bash:</b></u> <br><b>Bamboo Bo Stick:</b> Dmg 8, Dly 20. +1.00 Wt <br>This weapon is found in the Crypt of Dalnir off of A Kly Imprecator. This weapon costs 100-200pp<br><br><b>Adamantite Bo Stick:</b> Dmg 19, Dly 30. +6.50 Wt <br>This weapon is found in either The Crypt of Dalnir off of A Kly Imprecator, or Old Sebilis off of Froglok Krup Shaman. This weapon costs 800-1100pp.<br><br><br>               <u><b>Hand To Hand</b></u><br><b>Polished Steel Ulak</b> Dmg 9, Dly 27. +3 Str +3 Wis +3 vsMg +25 HP +25 Mana +1.10 Wt<br>This weapon is found in Dawnshroud Peaks off of A Tribal Lookout. This weapon costs 30-50pp.<br><br><b>Khaliz's Katar</b> Dmg 6, Dly 27. +1 Agi +1 Dex +1 vsCold +15 HP +1.30 Wt <br>This weapon is found in Netherbian Lair and drops off of a Mature Fungoid. This weapon sells for about 15pp.<br><br><br>Although some of these weapons cost an amount of money that a new Everquest player will not have for quite sometime, do not hesitate to loot and use a Splintering Club or a Cracked Staff from a Decaying Skeleton, or buy one from a vendor for about 1pp. These two weapons may not be better damage dealers than your fists, but getting and maintaining all 3 skills (Hand to Hand, 1 Hand Bash, and 2 Hand Bash) at your skill level is very important.<br><br>So long, and good luck on your quest for weapons.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Jul 26 12:30:39 2002</em></p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Ssalizka Sss'ra<br>57 Iksar Monk<br>Vazaelle <br> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286441" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286441</a></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
